<p>Ф⌡╢Е╪╨Е╓╖Г └Ф≤╞О╪▄Е°╗Ф≈═ФЁ∙Х╝©И≈╝Г╫▒Г╩°Ф≈╤О╪▄Flipkart Lite Е▐╞Д╩╔Е┐▐Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╦─Ф═╥Г┘╖Е╦╦Ф┴╖Х║▄О╪▄Х©≤Д╪ Е╬┬И╙ Ф╟■Г └Е▐≤Ф┬░И╩▒Г≥╫Х┴╡О╪⌡Д╦█Д╫├Е╕┌Ф╜╓О╪▄Ф⌡╬Г╩▐Х╝©И≈╝Х©┤Г └Е∙├Е⌠│И┐╫Д╪ Х╒╚Г╪⌠Е╜≤Д╦▀Ф²╔Е╬≈Д╩╔Е°╗Г╕╩Г╨©Ф≈╤Г╩╖Г╩╜Х╝©И≈╝Ц─┌Е°╗Е∙├Е⌠│И≥█Д╩╥Ц─│Д©┐И■─Г╜┴Ф≈╤Е┬╩О╪▄Flipkart Lite Д╪ Е┐▐Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╦─Ф═╥Е▐▒Х╣╥Ф▌╗И─│И─ Г÷╔О╪▄Е░╦Е╪∙Г■╗Ф┬╥Е⌡·Е┬╟Е╨■Г■╗Ц─┌</p>

<p><strong>Ф≈═И°─Ф▀┘Е©┐Г╫▒Г╩°Е╩╤Х©÷О╪⌡Ф°┴Г²─Г▀╛Г╚▀Е┘╔Е▐ёД╦▌Г▀╛Г╚▀Г └Д©²Ф╢╩Ф°╨Е┬╤Ц─┌</strong>Д╧▀Е┴█Д╦╓Д╦╙И≈╝И╒≤Г └Д╦─Е╧╤Х╖ёЕ├ЁО╪▄Е╝ёЕ▒┼Г²─ web Е╨■Г■╗Е°╗Г╖╩Е┼╗Х╝╬Е╓┤Д╦┼Г └Ф╣╢Г│╚И┤█Г■÷О╪ Ф╩║Х╤Ё PWA Ф╗║Е·▀Г └ web Е╨■Г■╗О╪▄Е╟├И─░Ф╦░Ф┬░Д╦╨Г╖╩Е┼╗Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷Г └Д╦─Г╜┴Е┘╛Ф╟▒О╪▄Е╧╤Е╟├Е░▒Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Е▐▒Х╣╥Ф▄▒Ф┬≤Д╦▌Ц─▄Е╓█Д╩┤Ц─█Ц─┌</p>

<p>Ф⌡╢Д╩╓Г╛■Х─┘Е┘╢Е╔▀Г └Ф≤╞О╪▄Е╟╠Е°╗Д╩┼Е╧╢ 11 Ф°┬Г └ <a href="https://youtu.be/eI3B6x0fw9s" title="Keynote (Chrome Dev Summit 2016)">Chrome Dev Summit 2016</a> Д╦┼О╪▄Chrome Г └Е╥╔Г╗▀ VP Darin Fisher Д╩▀Г╩█Д╨├ Chrome Е⌡╒И≤÷Ф╜ёЕ°╗Е│ Г └Д╦─Д╨⌡Е╝·И╙▄О╪ Ф┼┼Ц─▄Ф╥╩Е┼═Х┤ЁД╦╩Е╠▐Ц─█И┤█Е▒╫Е░█Д╦╨Ц─▄Е╝┴Хё┘Ц─█О╪▄Х╒╚Е╝┴Хё┘Г └ PWA Д╦█Е├█Д╩┘Д╩╔ widget Г └Е╫╒Е╪▐Ф≤╬Г╓╨Е°╗Ф║▄И²╒Д╦┼О╪▄Х─▄Ф≤╞Г°÷Ф╜ёЕ│ Е┬╟Д╦▌Ф┴─Ф°┴Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Е╧ЁГ╨╖О╪▄Д╦─Ф═╥Х╒╚Ф■╤Г╨ЁХ©⌡Е╨■Г■╗Ф┼╫Е╠┴О╪┬App DrawerО╪┴И┤▄О╪▄Д╦─Ф═╥Е┤╨Г▌╟Е°╗ГЁ╩Г╩÷Х╝╬Г╫╝Д╦╜ П÷▌┴П÷▌┴П÷▌┴Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/flipkart-3.jpeg" alt="" />
<em>Е⌡╬Г┴┤Ф²╔Ф╨░: Hux &amp; <a href="https://twitter.com/adityapunjani">@adityapunjani</a></em></p>

<p>Е⌡╬Д╦╜Д╩▌Е╥╕Е┬╟Е▐ЁЕ┬├Е┬╚Д╦╨О╪ Г╠╩Д╪╪Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е╝┴Хё┘Г∙▄И²╒О╪⌡Х╒╚Ф■╤Г╨ЁЕ°╗Е╨■Г■╗Ф┼╫Е╠┴И┤▄Г └ Flipkart Lite Д╦▌ Hux BlogО╪⌡Х╝╬Г╫╝Г∙▄И²╒Д╦╜Е╧╤Е┬≈Е┤╨Г▌╟Г └ Flipkart Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌ Flipkart Lite PWA О╪┬Е▐╞Д╩╔Г°▀Е┬╟ PWA Е╥╗Е╓╖Г └Д╫⌠Г╖╞Д╪≤Е┼©О╪┴</p>

<p><strong>Г╛■Х─┘Г⌡╦Д©║О╪▄PWA Ф╗║Е·▀Е╟├Г╩╖Г╨╕ 20 Е╧╢Е┴█Ф╗╙Г╘╨Е┤╨Д╦√Г └ Ajax Д╦▌Г╨╕ 10 Е╧╢Е┴█Иё▌И²║Г╖╩Е┼╗Д╨▓Х│■Г╫▒Г └Е⌠█Е╨■Е╪▐Х╝╬Х╝║Д╧▀Е░▌О╪▄Ф▌─Х╣╥ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф╗║Е·▀Г └Г╛╛Д╦┴Ф╛║Ф═╧Ф°╛Ф─╖И²╘Е▒╫О╪▄Е╟├ web Е╨■Г■╗Е╦╕Х©⌡Д╦─Д╦╙Е┘╗Ф√╟Г └Ф≈╤Д╩ёЦ─┌</strong></p>

<h2 id="pwa-Е┘ЁИ■╝Ф┼─Ф°╞Г └Е┴█Д╦√Д╩┼Г■÷">PWA Е┘ЁИ■╝Ф┼─Ф°╞Г └Е┴█Д╦√Д╩┼Г■÷</h2>

<h3 id="web-app-manifest"><a href="https://w3c.github.io/manifest/#use-cases-and-requirements" title="Web App Manifest">Web App Manifest</a></h3>

<p>Web App ManifestО╪▄Е█ЁИ─ Х©┤Д╦─Д╦╙Ф╦┘Е█∙Ф√┤Д╩╤Е░▒Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Ф ╢И°╡ web Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е┘┐Ф∙╟Ф█╝О╪▄Е▄┘Ф▀╛Е░█Е╜≈Ц─│icon Г └ URL Г╜┴О╪▄Д╩╔Е╓┤Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╫©Г■╗О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌Е°╗Ф╥╩Е┼═Х┤ЁД╦╩Е╠▐Ф┬√Ф▌╗И─│И─ Г÷╔Ф≈╤Ф ╢И°╡Г╩≥Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷О╪▄Д╩▌Х─▄Е╒·Е╪╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷Г └И⌡├Ф┬░Х┐╫Е┼⌡Ц─┌</p>

<p>Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Е°╗Г╖╩Е┼╗Х╝╬Е╓┤Д╦┼Г └Д╫⌠И╙▄Ф⌡╢Ф▌╔Х©▒Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е╟²Х╞∙Е┘╤Е╝·Ф≈╘Е°╗ 2008 Е╧╢Г └ <a href="https://huangxuan.me/pwa-qcon2016/#/37" title="PWA@QCon2016 #37">iOS 1.1.3 Д╦▌ iOS 2.1.0 </a>Ф≈╤Е╟╠Е╪─Е╖▀Д╨├О╪▄Е╝┐Д╩╛Е┬├Е┬╚Д╦╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Е╒·Е┼═Д╨├Е╞╧Х┤╙Е╝ Д╧┴ icon Е▓▄Е┘╗Е╠▐Ф┴⌠Е╪─Г └Ф■╞Ф▄│Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/ios2-a2hs.gif" alt="" />
<em>Е⌡╬Г┴┤Ф²╔Ф╨░: <a href="http://appleinsider.com/articles/08/10/03/latest_iphone_software_supports_full_screen_web_apps.html">appleinsider.com</a></em></p>

<p>Д╫├Ф≤╞Е╬┬Е©╚О╪▄И ▐Г²─Х╤┼Ф²╔Х╤┼Е╓ Г └Г╖│Ф°┴Е╧ЁЕ▐╟И─ Х©┤ <code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;meta&gt;</code>/<code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;link&gt;</code> Ф═┤Г╜╬Ф²╔Д╦╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф╥╩Е┼═Ц─▄Г╖│Х╢╖Ц─█О╪▄<code class="highlighter-rouge">&lt;head&gt;</code> Е╬┬Е©╚Е╟╠Х╒╚Е║·Ф╩║Д╨├О╪ </p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!-- Add to homescreen for Safari on iOS --&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"apple-mobile-web-app-capable"</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">"yes"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style"</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">"black"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"apple-mobile-web-app-title"</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">"Lighten"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>

<span class="c">&lt;!-- Add to homescreen for Chrome on Android --&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"mobile-web-app-capable"</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">"yes"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;mate</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"theme-color"</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">"#000000"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>

<span class="c">&lt;!-- Icons for iOS and Android Chrome M31~M38 --&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"apple-touch-icon-precomposed"</span> <span class="na">sizes=</span><span class="s">"144x144"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"images/touch/apple-touch-icon-144x144-precomposed.png"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"apple-touch-icon-precomposed"</span> <span class="na">sizes=</span><span class="s">"114x114"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"images/touch/apple-touch-icon-114x114-precomposed.png"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"apple-touch-icon-precomposed"</span> <span class="na">sizes=</span><span class="s">"72x72"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"images/touch/apple-touch-icon-72x72-precomposed.png"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"apple-touch-icon-precomposed"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"images/touch/apple-touch-icon-57x57-precomposed.png"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>

