  </span><span class="nl">"theme_color"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"#000"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"background_color"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"#fff"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">&lt;!-- document --&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"manifest"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"/manifest.json"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Х╞╦Е╕┌ <code class="highlighter-rouge">name</code>Ц─│<code class="highlighter-rouge">icons</code>Ц─│<code class="highlighter-rouge">display</code> И┐╫Ф≤╞Ф┬▒Д╩╛Ф╞■Х╬┐Г├÷Ф┌┴Г └О╪▄Х─▄Е╓╖И┐╗Е┬├Ф√╟Е╒·Г └Ф┬░Е▒≤Е┬≥Д╦╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Е╦╕Ф²╔Д╨├Д╦─ГЁ╩Е┬≈Д╩╔Е┴█ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф┐ЁЕ│ Е█╢Е│ Д╦█Е┬╟О╪┬Ф┬√Е°╗Д╧▀Е┴█Е▐╙Х┐╫И²═ hackО╪┴Г └Ф√╟Г┴╧Ф─╖О╪ </p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">scope</code>О╪ Е╝ Д╧┴Д╨├ web Е╨■Г■╗Г └Ф╣▐Х╖┬Д╫°Г■╗Е÷÷О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌Д╫°Г■╗Е÷÷Е╓√Г └ URL Е╟╠Д╪ Ф┴⌠Е╪─Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Х─▄Д╦█Д╪ Е°╗Е╫⌠Е┴█ PWA И┤▄Г╩╖Г╩╜Ф╣▐Х╖┬Ц─┌</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">start_url</code>О╪ Е╝ Д╧┴Д╨├Д╦─Д╦╙ PWA Г └Е┘╔Е▐ёИ║╣И²╒Ц─┌Ф╞■Е╕┌Х╞╢Д╫═Ф╥╩Е┼═ <a href="https://huangxuan.me" title="Hux Blog">Hux Blog</a> Г └Д╩╩Д╫∙Д╦─Д╦╙Ф√┤Г╚═Е┬╟Д╦╩Е╠▐О╪▄Д╩▌Д╦╩Е╠▐Ф┴⌠Е╪─Ф≈╤И┐╫Д╪ Х╝©И≈╝ <a href="https://huangxuan.me" title="Hux Blog">Hux Blog</a> Г └Д╦╩И║╣Ц─┌</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">orientation</code>О╪ Г╩┬Д╨▌О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔И■│Е╝ Е╠▐Е╧∙Ф≈▀Х╫╛Д╨├О╪┬Е√°Ф·│Х─▄ФЁёБ─╕О╪┴</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">theme_color</code>/<code class="highlighter-rouge">background_color</code>О╪ Д╦╩И╒≤Х┴╡Д╦▌Х┐▄Ф≥╞Х┴╡О╪▄Г■╗Д╨▌И┘█Г╫╝Д╦─Д╨⌡Е▐╞Е╝ Е┬╤Г └Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷ UI Д╩╔Ф▐░И╚≤Г■╗Ф┬╥Д╫⌠И╙▄О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌ Android Г └Г┼╤Ф─│Ф═▐Ц─│Д╩╩Е┼║Ф═▐Г╜┴Ц─┌</li>
</ul>

<p>Х©≥Д╦╙Ф╦┘Е█∙Г └Ф┬░Е▒≤Х©≤Ф°┴Е╬┬Е╓ О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌Г■╗Д╨▌Её╟Ф≤▌Ц─▄Е╞╧Е╨■Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ц─█Г └ <code class="highlighter-rouge">related_applications</code> Г╜┴Г╜┴О╪▄Ф°╛Ф√┤Е╟╠Д╦█Д╦─Д╦─Е┬≈Д╦╬Д╨├Ц─┌Д╫°Д╦╨ PWA Г └Ц─▄Ф┬╥Е▐ёФ°╛Ц─█О╪▄Ф┴©Х╫╫Г²─ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷И⌡├Ф┬░Х┐╫Е┼⌡Г └И┤█Д╩╩О╪▄Web App Manifest Х©≤Е╟├Е°╗Ф≈╔Е░▌Д╦█Ф√╜Ф┴╘Е╠∙О╪▄Д╩╔Ф╩║Х╤Ё web Е╨■Г■╗И╚≤И─÷Ф╪■Е▄√Г └И°─Х╕│Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="service-worker"><a href="https://w3c.github.io/ServiceWorker/" title="Service Worker">Service Worker</a></h3>

<p>Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▌÷Ф°┴Г └Ф∙╢Д╦╙ Web Е╨■Г■╗Ф╗║Е·▀О╪▄И┐╫Ф≤╞Ф·└Е╩╨Е°╗Ц─▄Г■╗Ф┬╥Х┐╫Д╦┼Г╫▒Ц─█Г └Е┴█Ф▐░Д╧▀Д╦▀Г └О╪▄Ф┴─Д╩╔Д╦─Г╕╩Г╨©Е╟╠Е▐╙Х┐╫Г▌╘Е╟▐Ф│░И╬≥Д╨├Ц─┌Е┘╤Е╝·О╪▄Е╞╧Д╨▌Ц─▄Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Г╕╩Г╨©Ф┴╖Х║▄Ц─█Х©≥Д╩╤Д╨▀О╪▄Service Worker Х┤ЁЕ╟▒Ф≤╞ web Г╓╬Е▄╨Г └Г╛╛Д╦┴Ф╛║Е╟²Х╞∙Д╨├Ц─┌</p>

<p>Ф∙┘Д╨▀Е▐╞Д╩╔Х©╫Ф╨╞Е┬╟ 2007 Е╧╢Г └ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Gears" title="Gears - Wikipedia">Google Gears</a>О╪ Д╦╨Д╨├Х╝╘Х┤╙Е╝╤Г └ GmailЦ─│YoutubeЦ─│Google Reader Г╜┴ web Е╨■Г■╗Е▐╞Д╩╔Е°╗Ф°╛Е°╟Е╜≤Е┌╗Ф∙╟Ф█╝Д╦▌Г╕╩Г╨©Ф┴╖Х║▄О╪▄Google Е╪─Е▐▒Д╨├Д╦─Д╦╙Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Ф▀⌠Е╠∙Ф²╔Е╒·Е╪╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Ц─┌Google Gears Ф■╞Ф▄│ IE 6Ц─│Safari 3Ц─│Firefox 1.5 Г╜┴Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗О╪⌡Х╕│Г÷╔И│⌠О╪▄И┌ёД╦─Е╧╢ Chrome И┐╫Х©≤Ф╡║Е┤╨Г■÷Е▒╒Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е°╗ Gears API Д╦╜О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛И─ Х©┤Е░▒ LocalServer Ф╗║Е²≈Ф▐░Д╨╓Д╦─Д╦╙Г╪⌠Е╜≤Ф√┤Д╩╤Ф╦┘Е█∙Ф²╔Е╝·Г▌╟Г╕╩Г╨©Ф■╞Ф▄│О╪ </p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// Somewhere in your javascript</span>
<span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">localServer</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">google</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">gears</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">factory</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">create</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">bata.localserver</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">store</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">localServer</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">createManagedStore</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">STORE_NAME</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="nx">store</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">manifestUrl</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">manifest.json</span><span class="dl">"</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// manifest.json</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">betaManifestVersion</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>
  <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">version</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">1.0</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">,</span>
  <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">entries</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[</span>
    <span class="p">{</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">url</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">index.html</span><span class="dl">"</span> <span class="p">},</span> 
    <span class="p">{</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">url</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">main.js</span><span class="dl">"</span> <span class="p">}</span>
  <span class="p">]</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Ф≤╞Д╦█Ф≤╞Ф└÷Е┬╟Е╬┬Г├÷Ф┌┴О╪÷Е╔╫Е┐▐ <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/2011/WD-html5-20110525/offline.html" title="HTML5 5.6 Offline Web Applications">HTML5 Х╖└Х▄┐</a>Д╦╜Г └ Application Cache Д╧÷Ф≤╞Г╠╩Д╪╪Г └Д╦°Х╔©О╪÷</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;html</span> <span class="na">manifest=</span><span class="s">"cache.appcache"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>CACHE MANIFEST

CACHE:
index.html
main.js
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Ф≤╞Г └О╪▄Gears Г └ LocalServer Е╟╠Ф≤╞Е░▌Ф²╔Е╓╖Е╝╤Ф┴─Г├÷Г÷╔Г └ App Cache Г └Е┴█Х╨╚О╪▄Е╓╖Г╨╕Д╩▌ <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/offline-webapps/" title="Offline Web Applications">2008</a> Е╧╢Е╪─Е╖▀ W3C Е╟╠Е╪─Е╖▀Е╟²Х╞∙Е╟├ Gears Х©⌡Х║▄Ф═┤Е┤├Е▄√Д╨├О╪⌡И≥╓Д╨├ LocalServerО╪▄Gears Д╦╜Г■╗Д╨▌Ф▐░Д╬⌡Е╧╤Х║▄Х╝║Г╝≈Х┐╫Е┼⌡Г └ WorkerPool Ф╗║Е²≈Д╦▌Г■╗Д╨▌Ф▐░Д╬⌡Ф°╛Е°╟Ф∙╟Ф█╝Е╨⌠Д╦▌ SQL Ф■╞Ф▄│Г └ Database Ф╗║Е²≈Д╧÷Е┬├Е┬╚Ф≤╞Ф≈╔Е░▌ Web Worker Д╦▌ Web SQL DatabaseО╪┬Е░▌Х╒╚Е╨÷Е╪┐О╪┴Г └Е┴█Х╨╚Ц─┌</p>

<p>HTML5 App Cache Д╫°Д╦╨Г╛╛Д╨▄ФЁ╒Ц─▄Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Г╕╩Г╨©Ф┴╖Х║▄Ц─█Г └Е╟²Х╞∙О╪▄Г║╝Е╝·Д╧÷Ф°█Е┼║Д╨├Ф╞■Е╕┌ Google DocЦ─│Е╟╓И⌡╗Ф╨╙Ф≈╘Е╧╢Д╫°Е⌠│ HTML5 ClearЦ─│Д╩╔Е▐┼Д╦─Г⌡╢Г■╗ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╫°Д╦╨Х┤╙Е╥╠ iOS Е╨■Г■╗Г └ FT.comО╪┬Financial TimesО╪┴Г╜┴Д╦█Е╟▒ web Е╨■Г■╗Ц─┌И┌ёД╧┬О╪▄Х©≤Ф°┴ Service Worker Д╩─Д╧┬Д╨▀Е▒╒О╪÷</p>

<p>Ф≤╞Е∙┼О╪▄Е╕┌Ф·° App Cache Ф╡║Ф°┴Х╒╚Х╝╬Х╝║Е╬≈<a href="https://huangxuan.me/sw-101-gdgdf/#/12" title="SW-101@DevFest #12">Г┐┌Е┬╟Е╝▄Е┘╗Д╦█Е▐╞Г╪√Г╗▀Ц─│Ф≈═ФЁ∙Ф╦┘Г░├Г╪⌠Е╜≤Ц─│Е┤═Д╧▌Ф╡║Ф°┴Х╥╞Г■╠Ф°╨Е┬╤Ц─│Е┤╨Д╨├ Bug Д╦─Г┌╧Ф∙▒И┐╫Ф╡║Ф°┴</a>О╪▄Е▐╞Х┐╫Е╟╠Г°÷Ф╡║ Service Worker Д╩─Д╧┬Д╨▀Д╨├Ц─┌<a href="https://huangxuan.me/sw-101-gdgdf/#/13" title="SW-101@DevFest #13">App Cache Е╥╡Г╩▐Е°╗Е┴█Д╦█Д╧┘Е╝ Г╗©Г └ HTML5.1 Д╦╜Х╒╚Ф▀©Ф▌┴Д╨├О╪▄W3C Д╦╨Д╨├Ф▄╫Ф∙▒ web Д╦√Г∙▄Г°÷Ф≤╞Д╦█Ф┐°Ф┼┼Х┤╙Е╥╠Г └Х└╦И┐╫Ф┴⌠Х┌©Д╨├Б─╕Б─╕</a></p>

<p>Ф≈╤Х┤ЁД╩┼Ф≈╔О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г╩┬Д╨▌Х©▌Ф²╔Д╨├ Service Worker Г └Ф⌡≥Е┘┴Ц─┌Г╝─Е█∙Ф²╔Х╞╢О╪▄Service Worker Ф≤╞Д╦─Д╦╙Е▐╞Г╪√Г╗▀Г └ Web WorkerО╪▄Е╝┐Е╟╠Е┐▐Д╦─Д╦╙Д╫█Д╨▌Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦▌Г╫▒Г╩°Д╧▀И≈╢Г └Е╝╒Ф┬╥Г╚╞Д╩ёГ░├О╪▄Е▐╞Д╩╔Ф▀╕Ф┬╙Ц─│Е╓└Г░├Ц─│Е⌠█Е╨■Ф╣│Г╩▐Г └ HTTP Х╞╥Ф╠┌О╪⌡И┘█Е░┬И ▐Д╧▀Е╪∙Е┘╔ Cache Storage APIО╪▄Д╫═Е▐╞Д╩╔Х┤╙Г■╠Г╝║Г░├ HTTP Х╞╥Ф╠┌Ф√┤Д╩╤Г╡▓Е╨╕Г └Г╪⌠Е╜≤О╪▄Х©≥Д╫©Е╬≈ Service Worker Е▐╞Д╩╔Д╩▌Г╪⌠Е╜≤Д╦╜Е░▒ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф▐░Д╬⌡Х╣└Ф╨░О╪▄Е█ЁД╫©Ф≤╞Е°╗Г╕╩Г╨©Г └Г▌╞Е╒┐Д╦▀Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/sw-sw.png" alt="" />
<em>Service Worker Е╟╠Е┐▐Д╦─Д╦╙Х©░Х║▄Е°╗Е╝╒Ф┬╥Г╚╞Г └Д╩ёГ░├</em></p>

<p>Ф╞■Е╕┌Х╞╢О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔Г╩≥Г╫▒И║╣ <code class="highlighter-rouge">foo.html</code> ФЁ╗Е├▄Х©≥Д╧┬Д╦─Д╦╙ Service WorkerО╪▄Е╝┐Е╟├Е┼╚Ф▄│Г■╠ <code class="highlighter-rouge">foo.html</code> Е▐▒Х╣╥Г └Д╦─Е┬┤ HTTP Х╞╥Ф╠┌О╪▄Е╧╤Г╩÷Г╩÷Х©■Е⌡·Ф°╙Х╝╬Г╫╝ <code class="highlighter-rouge">Content-Type</code> Г └ <code class="highlighter-rouge">Hello World!</code>О╪ </p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// sw.js</span>
<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">onfetch</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">respondWith</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">new</span> <span class="nx">Response</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">Hello World!</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Service Worker Г╛╛Д╦─Ф╛║Е▐▒Е╦┐Д╨▌ 2014 Е╧╢Г └ Google IO Д╦┼О╪▄Г⌡╝Е┴█Е╥╡Е╓└Д╨▌ W3C Е╥╔Д╫°Х█┴Ф║┬Г └Г┼╤Ф─│Ц─┌Е┘╤Х╝╬Х╝║Е░╦Е▐√Д╨├ Application Cache Г └Е╓╠Х╢╔Г╩▐И╙▄О╪▄Д╫°Д╦╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е╪─Е▐▒Х─┘Г └Д╫═Ф°┴Г²─Е╝▄Е┘╗Г └Ф▌╖Е┬╤Х┐╫Е┼⌡О╪⌡Е░▄Ф≈╤О╪▄Е╝┐Х©≤Е─÷И┴╢Д╨├ Chrome Е╓ Е╧╢Ф²╔Е°╗ Chrome Extension Д╦┼Г └Х╝╬Х╝║Г╩▐И╙▄О╪┬Chrome Background Pages Д╦▌ Chrome Event PagesО╪┴О╪▄И┤┤Г■╗Д╨├Е÷╨Д╨▌Ц─▄Д╨▀Д╩╤И╘╠Е┼╗Ц─█Г └Е■╓И├▓Ф°╨Е┬╤О╪▄Д╩╔Е╓╖Е╧┘Х┼┌Г°│Е░▌Е▐╟Х╝║Г╝≈Г └Х┐╫Х─≈Ц─┌Ф╞■Е╕┌Д╦┼И²╒Г └ <code class="highlighter-rouge">fetch</code> Е┘╤Е╝·Е╟╠Ф≤╞Д╪ Е■╓И├▓ Service Worker Г └Д╨▀Д╩╤Д╧▀Д╦─Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/sw-lifecycle.png" alt="" />
<em>Service Worker Г └Г■÷Е▒╫Е▒╗Ф°÷</em></p>

<p>И≥╓Д╨├Г╠╩Д╪╪ <code class="highlighter-rouge">fetch</code> Х©≥Ф═╥Г └Е┼÷Х┐╫Д╨▀Д╩╤Е╓√О╪▄Service Worker Х©≤Ф▐░Д╬⌡Д╨├Д╦─Г╩└Г■÷Е▒╫Е▒╗Ф°÷Д╨▀Д╩╤О╪▄Е▄┘Ф▀╛Е╝┴Хё┘Ц─│Ф©─Ф╢╩Г╜┴Г╜┴Ц─┌Ф╞■Е╕┌О╪▄Е°╗ Service Worker Г └Ц─▄Е╝┴Хё┘Ц─█Д╨▀Д╩╤Д╦╜О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔Ф┼┼ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф┴─И°─Х╕│Г └Х╣└Ф╨░Г╩÷Г╩÷И╒└Е┘┬Д╦▀Х╫╫Е╧╤Г╪⌠Е╜≤Е┬╟ Cache Storage Д╦╜Е▌╩О╪ </p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// sw.js</span>
<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">oninstall</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">waitUntil</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="nx">caches</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">installation</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">)</span>
      <span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">then</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">cache</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span>  <span class="nx">cache</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">addAll</span><span class="p">([</span>
        <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">./</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">./styles.css</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">./script.js</span><span class="dl">'</span>
      <span class="p">]))</span>
  <span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Х©≥Ф═╥О╪▄Е╫⌠Г■╗Ф┬╥Г╕╩Г╨©О╪▄Г╫▒Г╩°Ф≈═ФЁ∙Х╝©И≈╝Ф≈╤О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е╟╠Е▐╞Д╩╔Д╩▌Г╪⌠Е╜≤Д╦╜Е░╞Е┼╗Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г └ web Е╨■Г■╗О╪ </p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">//sw.js</span>
<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">onfetch</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">fetched</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">fetch</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">request</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">cached</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">caches</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">match</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">request</span><span class="p">)</span>

  <span class="nx">e</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">respondWith</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="nx">fetched</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="k">catch</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">_</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="nx">cached</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Е▐╞Д╩╔Г°▀Е┤╨О╪▄Service Worker Х╒╚Х╝╬Х╝║Д╦╨Д╦─Д╦╙Г⌡╦Е╞╧Е╨∙Е╠┌О╪┬low-levelО╪┴Ц─│И╚≤Е╨╕Е▐╞Г╪√Г╗▀Ц─│Е╜░Ф╕┌Е©╣Д╪≈Е╓ О╪▄Д╧÷Е⌡═Ф╜╓Е╪┌Е╦╦Г│╣Ф╢╩Д╦■Е╪╨Е╓╖Г └ APIО╪▄Ф∙┘Ф°╛Ф√┤Е▐╙Х┐╫Е╠∙Г╓╨Е╝┐Г └Е├╟Е╠╠Д╦─Х╖▓Ц─┌Е┤╨Д╨▌Е╝┴Е┘╗Х─┐Х≥▒О╪▄ФЁ╗Е├▄ Service Worker Х╕│Ф╠┌Д╫═Г └ web Е╨■Г■╗И┐╗Г╫╡Д╨▌ HTTPS Е█▐Х╝╝Д╦▀О╪▄Д╩╔Е┘█Е┬╘Г■╗ Service Worker Г └Д╦╜И≈╢Д╨╨Ф■╩Е┤╩Ц─┌Г╛■Х─┘Е°╗Д╩┼Е╧╢ GDG Е▄≈Д╨╛Г └ DevFest Д╦┼Е┬├Д╨╚Д╨├ <a href="https://huangxuan.me/2016/11/20/sw-101-gdgdf/">Service Worker 101</a>О╪▄Ф╤╣Г⌡√Д╨├ Service Worker Х╜╛Е╕┌Ц─▄Г╫▒Г╩°Д╪≤Е┘┬Ц─█Ц─│Ц─▄Г╪⌠Е╜≤Д╪≤Е┘┬Ц─█Ц─│Ц─▄Г╫▒Г╩°Д╦▌Г╪⌠Е╜≤Ф╞■Х╣⌡Ц─█Х©≥Д╨⌡Ф⌡╢Е╓█Ф²┌Г └Г╪⌠Е╜≤Г╜√Г∙╔Ц─│Е╜╕Д╧═Х╣└Ф√≥Ц─│Д╩╔Е▐┼<a href="https://github.com/Huxpro/sw-101-gdgdf">Г╓╨Д╬▀Д╩ёГ═│</a>О╪▄Е▐╞Д╩╔Д╬⌡Е╓╖Е╝╤Е▐┌Х─┐Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/sw-race.png" alt="" />
<em>Service Worker Г └Д╦─Г╖█Г╪⌠Е╜≤Г╜√Г∙╔О╪ Х╝╘Г╫▒Г╩°Х╞╥Ф╠┌Д╦▌Х╞╩Е▐√Г╪⌠Е╜≤Ф╞■Х╣⌡</em></p>

<p>Д╫═Д╧÷Е▐╞Д╩╔Е╟²Х╞∙Е°╗Ф■╞Ф▄│ PWA Г └Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦╜Х╝©И≈╝Г╛■Х─┘Г └Е█ Е╝╒ <a href="https://huangxuan.me" title="Hux Blog">Hux Blog</a>О╪▄Ф└÷Е▐≈ Service Worker Г └Е╝·И≥┘Ф∙┬Ф·°О╪ Ф┴─Ф°┴Х╝©И≈╝Х©┤Г └И║╣И²╒И┐╫Д╪ Х╒╚Г╪⌠Е╜≤Е╧╤Е┘│Х╝╦Е°╗Г╕╩Г╨©Г▌╞Е╒┐Д╦▀Г╩╖Г╩╜Х╝©И≈╝О╪▄Ф┴─Ф°┴Ф°╙Х╝©И≈╝Х©┤Г └И║╣И²╒Е┬≥Д╪ Е°╗Г╕╩Г╨©Г▌╞Е╒┐Д╦▀Е╠∙Г╓╨Д╦─Д╦╙Х┤╙Е╝ Д╧┴Г └Г╕╩Г╨©И║╣И²╒Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е°╗Г╛■Х─┘Г°▀Ф²╔О╪▄<strong>Service Worker Е╞╧ PWA Г └И┤█Х╕│Ф─╖Г⌡╦Е╫⌠Д╨▌ <code class="highlighter-rouge">XMLHTTPRequest</code> Д╧▀Д╨▌ AjaxО╪▄Е╙▓Д╫⌠Ф÷╔Х╞╒О╪┬Media QueryО╪┴Д╧▀Д╨▌Е⌠█Е╨■Е╪▐Х╝╬Х╝║О╪▄Ф≤╞Ф■╞Ф▓▒ PWA Д╫°Д╦╨Ц─▄Д╦▀Д╦─Д╩ё web Е╨■Г■╗Ф╗║Е·▀Ц─█Г └Ф°─Ф═╦Е©┐Ф┼─Ф°╞Ц─┌</strong>Г■╠Д╨▌ Service Worker Е▐╞Д╩╔Д╦▌Е▄┘Ф▀╛ Indexed DBЦ─│Streams Е°╗Е├┘Г └Е╓╖И┐╗Е┬├ DOM Ф≈═Е┘Ё API Х©⌡Х║▄Д╨╓Д╨▓О╪▄Е╝┐Г └Ф╫°Е┼⌡Г╝─Г⌡╢Ф≈═Е▐╞И≥░И┤▐Ц─┌Г╛■Х─┘Е┤═Д╧▌Е▐╞Д╩╔Ф√╜Х╗─О╪▄Service Worker Е╟├Е°╗Ф°╙Ф²╔Е█│Е╧╢И┤▄Ф┬░Д╦╨ web Е╝╒Ф┬╥Г╚╞Ф┼─Ф°╞Е╥╔Г╗▀Е▄√Г └Е┘╣Е╝╤Е©┘Д╨┴Д╧▀Е°╟О╪▄Е╦╕Ф²╔Ц─▄Г╕╩Г╨©Д╪≤Е┘┬О╪┬Offline-firstО╪┴Ц─█Г └Ф·╤Ф·└И²╘Е▒╫Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="push-notification">Push Notification</h3>

<p>PWA Ф▌╗И─│И─ Г÷╔Д╦╜Г └Ц─▄Ф▌╗И─│Ц─█Д╦▌Ц─▄И─ Г÷╔Ц─█О╪▄Е┘╤Е╝·Д╫©Г■╗Г └Ф≤╞Д╦╓Д╦╙Д╦█Е░▄Д╫├Е▐┬Г⌡╦Е╬≈Г⌡┼Е╫╟Г └ APIО╪ </p>

<p><a href="https://notifications.spec.whatwg.org/" title="Notification API">Notification API</a> Г⌡╦Д©║Е╓╖Е╝╤Е╧╤Д╦█И≥▄Г■÷О╪▄Е╝┐Х╢÷Х╢ёФ┴─Ф°┴Д╦▌И─ Г÷╔Ф°╛Х╨╚Г⌡╦Е┘ЁГ └Ф°╨Е┬╤О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌И─ Г÷╔Г └Ф²┐И≥░Г╝║Г░├Ц─│Е░▒Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷Е▐▒Х╣╥И─ Г÷╔Ц─│И─ Г÷╔Г └Г╠╩Е·▀Д╦▌И÷ЁФ∙┬О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼Ф▐░Д╬⌡И─ Г÷╔Х╒╚Г┌╧Е┤╩Ф┬√Е┘ЁИ≈╜Ф≈╤Г └Е⌡·Х╟┐Г╜┴Г╜┴О╪▄Г⌡╝Е┴█Е⌡╫Е├┘Е╓√Г └Е░└Е╓╖Г╫▒Г╚≥О╪┬Е╟╓Е┘╤Е°╗Ф║▄И²╒Г╚╞О╪┴И┐╫Ф°┴Д╦─Е╝ Г └Д╫©Г■╗Ц─┌Notification API Ф°─Ф≈╘Е╨■Х╞╔Ф≤╞Е°╗ <a href="https://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/notifications/quick/" title="Using the Notification API">2010</a> Е╧╢Е┴█Е░▌Г■╠ Chromium Ф▐░Е┤╨<a href="http://www.chromium.org/developers/design-documents/desktop-notifications/api-specification" title="API Specification - The Chromium Projects">Х█┴Ф║┬</a>Д╩╔ <code class="highlighter-rouge">webkitNotifications</code> Е┴█Г╪─Ф√╧Е╪▐Е╝·Г▌╟О╪⌡И ▐Г²─ 2011 Е╧╢Х©⌡Е┘╔Ф═┤Е┤├Е▄√О╪⌡2012 Е╧╢Е°╗ Safari 6О╪┬Mac OSX 10.8+О╪┴Д╦┼Х▌╥Е╬≈Ф■╞Ф▄│О╪⌡2015 Е╧╢ Notification API Ф┬░Д╦╨ <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/notifications/" title="Web Notifications - W3C">W3C Recommendation</a>О╪⌡2016 Е╧╢ <a href="https://blogs.windows.com/msedgedev/2016/05/16/web-notifications-microsoft-edge/#2VBm890EjvAvUcgE.97">Edge Г └Ф■╞Ф▄│</a>О╪⌡Web Notifications Е╥╡Г╩▐Е°╗Ф║▄И²╒Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦╜Х▌╥Е╬≈Д╨├Е┘╗И²╒Ф■╞Ф▄│О╪┬ChromeЦ─│EdgeЦ─│FirefoxЦ─│OperaЦ─│SafariО╪┴Г └Ф┬░Е╟╠Ц─┌</p>

<p><a href="http://w3c.github.io/push-api/" title="Push API">Push API</a> Г └Е┤╨Г▌╟Е┬≥Х╝╘Ф▌╗И─│Ф°█Е┼║Е┘╥Е╓┤Д╨├Е░▒ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф▌╗И─│Ф╤┬Ф│╞Г └Х┐╫Е┼⌡О╪▄Е╝┐Е╝ Д╧┴Д╨├ web Е╨■Г■╗Е╕┌Д╫∙Е░▒Ф▌╗И─│Ф°█Е┼║Е▐▒Х╣╥Х╝╒И≤┘Ц─│Е╕┌Д╫∙Е⌠█Е╨■Ф▌╗И─│Ф╤┬Ф│╞О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼ web Е╨■Г■╗Ц─│Е╨■Г■╗Ф°█Е┼║Е≥╗Д╦▌Ф▌╗И─│Ф°█Е┼║Д╧▀И≈╢Г └И┴╢Ф²┐Д╦▌Е┼═Е╞├Ф°╨Е┬╤О╪⌡Г■╠Д╨▌ Push API Е╧╤Д╦█Д╬²Х╣√ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗ UI Е╜≤Ф╢╩О╪▄Ф┴─Д╩╔Е█ЁД╫©Ф≤╞Е°╗ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Ф°╙Х╒╚Г■╗Ф┬╥Ф┴⌠Е╪─Г └Ф≈╤Е─≥О╪▄Д╧÷Е▐╞Д╩╔И─ Х©┤Е░▌Е▐╟Х©⌡Г╗▀Ф▌╔Е▐≈Ф▌╗И─│Ф╤┬Ф│╞Е╧╤Х╟┐Г■╗ Notification API Е░▒Г■╗Ф┬╥Е▐▒Е┤╨И─ Г÷╔Ц─┌Е─╪Е╬≈Д╦─Ф▐░Г └Ф≤╞О╪▄Mac OSX 10.9 Mavericks Д╦▌ Safari 7 Е°╗ 2013 Е╧╢Е╟╠Е▐▒Е╦┐Д╨├Х┤╙Е╥╠Г └Г╖│Ф°┴Ф▌╗И─│Ф■╞Ф▄│О╪▄Е÷╨Д╨▌ APNS Г └ <a href="https://developer.apple.com/notifications/safari-push-notifications/" title="Safari Push Notifications">Safari Push Notifications</a>Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е°╗ PWA Д╦╜О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е┬╘Г■╗ Service Worker Г └Е░▌Е▐╟Х╝║Г╝≈Х┐╫Е┼⌡Г╩⌠Е░┬ Push API Е╞╧Ф▌╗И─│Д╨▀Д╩╤Х©⌡Х║▄Е⌠█Е╨■О╪▄Е╧╤И─ Х©┤ Notification API Е╝·Г▌╟И─ Г÷╔Г └Е▐▒Е┤╨Д╦▌Е╓└Г░├О╪ </p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// sw.js</span>
<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">addEventListener</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">push</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">event</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nx">event</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">waitUntil</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="c1">// Process the event and display a notification.</span>
    <span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">registration</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">showNotification</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">Hey!</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">});</span>

<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">addEventListener</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">notificationclick</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">event</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>  
  <span class="c1">// Do something with the event  </span>
  <span class="nx">event</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">notification</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">close</span><span class="p">();</span>  
<span class="p">});</span>

<span class="nb">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">addEventListener</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">notificationclose</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">event</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>  
  <span class="c1">// Do something with the event  </span>
<span class="p">});</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Е╞╧Д╨▌ Push NotificationО╪▄Г╛■Х─┘Г └Е┤═Ф╛║Е┬├Д╨╚Д╦╜Д╦─Г⌡╢И┐╫Ф▐░Г └Г╗█Е╬╝Е╟▒Д╦─Д╨⌡О╪▄Д╦─Ф≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨ Push API Х©≤Е╓└Д╨▌ Editor Draft Г └Г┼╤Ф─│О╪▄Д╨▄Ф≤╞Г⌡╝Е┴█Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦▌Ф▌╗И─│Ф°█Е┼║И≈╢Г └Е█▐Х╝╝Ф■╞Ф▄│Х©≤Д╦█Е╓÷Ф┬░Г├÷О╪ ChromeО╪┬Д╦▌Е┘╤Е╝┐Е÷╨Д╨▌ Blink Г └Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗О╪┴Е°╗ Chromium 52 Д╧▀Е┴█Е▐╙Ф■╞Ф▄│Е÷╨Д╨▌ Google Г╖│Ф°┴Г └ GCM/FCM Ф°█Е┼║Х©⌡Х║▄И─ Г÷╔Ф▌╗И─│Ц─┌Д╦█Х©┤Е╔╫Ф╤┬Ф│╞Ф≤╞О╪▄Г╩╖ Firefox 44 Д╧▀Е░▌О╪▄Chrome 52 Д╦▌ Opera 39 Д╧÷Г╢╖Х©╫Е┘╤Е░▌Е╝·Г▌╟Д╨├Ф╜ёЕ°╗Г■╠ IETF Х©⌡Х║▄Ф═┤Е┤├Е▄√Г └ <a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-webpush-protocol-12" title="Web Push Protocol">Web Ф▌╗И─│Е█▐Х╝╝О╪┬Web Push ProtocolО╪┴</a>Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е╕┌Ф·°Д╫═Е╥╡Г╩▐Е°╗Д╫©Г■╗ Google Г └Д╨▒Ф°█Е┼║О╪┬Ф╞■Е╕┌ FirebaseО╪┴О╪▄Е╧╤Д╦■Д╦╩Х╕│И²╒Е░▒Г └Ф≤╞Ф╣╥Е╓√Г■╗Ф┬╥О╪▄И┌ёД╧┬Е°╗ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦┼Ф■╞Ф▄│Е÷╨Д╨▌ GCM/FCM Г └Ф▌╗И─│И─ Г÷╔Е╧╤Д╦█Ф≤╞Д╦─Д╩╤Х╢╧Е┼⌡Г └Д╨▀Ф┐┘О╪▄Г╛■Х─┘Ф▌╗Х█░Д╫═И≤┘Х╞╩Д╦─Д╦▀ Google Developers Г └<a href="https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/engage-and-retain/push-notifications/" title="Web Push Notifications - Google Developer">ГЁ╩Е┬≈Ф√┤Г╚═</a>О╪▄Е╬┬Е╓ Е⌡╫Е╓√Е┘╛Е▐╦Е╥╡Г╩▐Г▌╘Х╣╥Ф²╔Д╨├Ц─┌</p>

<h2 id="Д╩▌-hybrid-Е┬╟-pwaД╩▌Е╟│И≈╜Е┬╟Е╪─Ф■╬">Д╩▌ Hybrid Е┬╟ PWAО╪▄Д╩▌Е╟│И≈╜Е┬╟Е╪─Ф■╬</h2>

<p>2008 Е╧╢О╪▄Е╫⌠Г╖╩Е┼╗Ф≈╤Д╩ёФ²╔Д╦╢О╪▄<a href="https://huangxuan.me/pwa-qcon2016/#/17" title="PWA@QCon2016 #17">Е■╠Х║╟Г╖╩Е┼╗ Web Г └Её╟И÷Ё</a>Е╪─Е╖▀Е┤╨Г▌╟О╪▄Х─▄Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Г └Х©⌡Е▄√Е╧╤Д╦█Х┐╫Х╥÷Д╦┼Ф≈╤О╪▄Ф²╔Х┤╙ Nitobi Г └ Brian Leroux Г╜┴Д╨╨Е┬⌡И─═Д╨├ <a href="https://cordova.apache.org/" title="Apache Cordova">Phonegap</a>О╪▄Е╦▄Ф°⌡Е╝┐Х┐╫Д╩╔ Polyfill Г └Е╫╒Е╪▐Ц─│Е╪╔Х║╔Г⌡╝Е┴█Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦▌Г╖╩Е┼╗Х╝╬Е╓┤И≈╢Г └Ц─▄И╦©Ф╡÷Ц─█О╪▄Д╩▌Ф╜╓Е╪─Е░╞Д╨├<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_web_app#Hybrid_Apps">Ф╥╥Е░┬Е╨■Г■╗О╪┬Hybrid AppsО╪┴</a>Г └Ф≈╤Д╩ёЦ─┌</p>

<p>Е┤═Е╧╢И≈╢О╪▄<a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/air.html" title="Adobe AIR Application">Adobe AIR</a>Ц─│<a href="https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/apps/br211385.aspx" title="Windows Runtime JS API">Windows Runtime Apps</a>Ц─│<a href="https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/apps" title="Chrome Packaged Apps">Chrome Apps</a>Ц─│<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Archive/Firefox_OS/Firefox_OS_apps/Building_apps_for_Firefox_OS" title="Firefox OS Packaged Apps">Firefox OS</a>Ц─│<a href="http://www.openwebosproject.org/" title="Open webOS">WebOS</a>Ц─│<a href="https://cordova.apache.org/" title="Apache Cordova">Cordova/Phonegap</a>Ц─│<a href="http://electron.atom.io/" title="Electron">Electron</a> Д╩╔Е▐┼Е⌡╫Е├┘Ф╞■Е╕┌Е╬╝Д©║Ц─│Ф╥≤Е╝²О╪▄Ф≈═Ф∙╟Г └ Hybrid Ф√╧Ф║┬Ф▀■Е°╟Х─▄Х╣╥О╪▄Х╝╘ web Е╪─Е▐▒Х─┘Е▐╞Д╩╔Е°╗Г╩╖Г╩╜Д╫©Г■╗ web Е╝╒Ф┬╥Г╚╞Ф┼─Ф°╞Г └Е░▄Ф≈╤О╪▄Е│ Е┬╟Д╦─Д╨⌡Е▐╙Ф°┴Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ф┴█Х┐╫Е│ Е┬╟Г └Д╨▀Ф┐┘О╪▄Е▄┘Ф▀╛Х╝©И≈╝Д╦─Д╨⌡Х╝╬Е╓┤Д╦▌Ф⌠█Д╫°ГЁ╩Г╩÷ APIО╪▄Г╩≥Г■╗Ф┬╥Е╦╕Ф²╔Ф⌡╢Е┼═ Ц─▄AppyЦ─█ Г └Д╫⌠И╙▄О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼Х©⌡Е┘╔ App Store Г╜┴Г╜┴Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/qcon-hybridzation.png" alt="" />
<em>Д╪≈Е╓ Г └ Hybrid Ф√╧Ф║┬</em></p>

<p>PWA Д╫°Д╦╨Д╦─Д╦╙Ф╤╣Г⌡√Ф─╖Ф°╞Х╞╜О╪▄Д╦▌Х©┤Е╬─Г └Х©≥Д╨⌡Ф┬√Е╓ Ф┬√Е╟▒И─ Х©┤Г╖│Ф°┴Е╧ЁЕ▐╟ API Е╒·Е╪╨ web Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е╟²Х╞∙Ф°─Е╓╖Г └Д╦█Е░▄О╪▄Е°╗Д╨▌Ф·└Ф┬░ PWA Г └Ф╞▐Д╦─И║╧Е÷╨Ф°╛Ф┼─Ф°╞О╪▄И┐╫Е╥╡Г╩▐Ф┬√Ф╜ёЕ°╗Х╒╚ IETFЦ─│ECMAЦ─│W3C Ф┬√ WHATWG Ф═┤Е┤├Е▄√О╪▄Д╦█Е┤╨Ф└▐Е╓√Г └Х╞²О╪▄Е╝┐Д╩╛И┐╫Е╟├Х╒╚Г╨ЁЕ┘╔Е╪─Ф■╬ web Ф═┤Е┤├О╪▄Е╧╤Е°╗Д╦█Х©°Г └Е╟├Ф²╔Е╬≈Е┬╟Ф┴─Ф°┴Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╦▌Е┘╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Г └Ф■╞Ф▄│Ц─┌Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г╩┬Д╨▌Е▐╞Д╩╔И─┐Е┤╨ App Store Е╟│И≈╜Г └Г╖≤Е╞├Х┼╠Е⌡╜О╪▄И┤█Ф√╟Е⌡·Е┬╟Е╠·Д╨▌ web Г └И┌ёГ┴┤Е╪─Ф■╬Х┤╙Г■╠Г └Е╓╖Е°╟Ц─┌</p>

<p>Ф°┴Х╤ёГ └Ф≤╞О╪▄Д╩▌Д╦┼Ф√┤Д╦╜Д╫═Д╧÷Е▐╞Д╩╔Е▐▒Г▌╟О╪▄Г╩└Ф┬░ PWA Г └Е░└И║╧Ф┼─Ф°╞Г └Х█┴Ф║┬Ф╜ёФ≤╞Г■╠Д╦┼Х©╟Е░└Г╖█Г╖│Ф°┴Ф√╧Ф║┬Х┐▄Е░▌Г └Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Е▌┌Е∙├Ф┬√Е╪─Е▐▒Х─┘Г⌡╢Ф▌╔Х╢║Г▄╝Ф┬√И≈╢Ф▌╔Е╫╠Е⌠█Г └Ц─┌Е▐╞Д╩╔Х╞╢О╪▄PWA Г └Х┐▄Е░▌Е╧╤Д╦█Ф≤╞Ф÷░Д╦─Е╝╤Ф┬√Д╦╓Е╝╤Е┘╛Е▐╦О╪▄Х─▄Ф≤╞Ф∙╢Д╦╙ web Г╓╬Е▄╨Д╦▌Ф∙╢Д╦╙ web Х╖└Х▄┐Ц─┌<strong>Ф╜ёФ≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨Х©≥Г╖█Е╪─Ф■╬Д╦▌Е▌╩Д╦╜Е©┐Е▄√Г └Е┼⌡И┤▐О╪▄Д╫©Е╬≈Д╦┤Г╩╢Г╫▒О╪┬World Wide WebО╪┴Х┐╫Е╓÷Ф┬░Д╦╨Е╫⌠Д╩┼Д╦√Г∙▄Д╦┼Х╥╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Х┐╫Е┼⌡Ф°─Е╪╨Ц─│Д╦■Е┤═Д╧▌Ф≤╞Е■╞Д╦─Д╦─Д╦╙Е┘╥Е╓┤Х©≥Г╖█Х╥╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Х┐╫Е┼⌡Г └Е╨■Г■╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Ц─┌</strong></p>

<p><a href="http://phonegap.com/blog/2012/05/09/phonegap-beliefs-goals-and-philosophy/" title="PhoneGap Beliefs, Goals, and Philosophy">Ц─▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г⌡╦Д©║ WebО╪▄Ф≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨Г⌡╦Д©║Е╝┐Ф≤╞Х╖ёЕ├ЁХ╝╬Е╓┤Е╥╝Е╪┌Е▄√Г └Г╩┬Ф·│Ф√╧Ф║┬О╪⌡Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г⌡╦Д©║О╪▄Е╫⌠ Web Е°╗Д╩┼Е╓╘Е│ Д╦█Е┬╟Д╦─Д╩╤Д╨▀Г └Ф≈╤Е─≥О╪▄Ф≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨Е╝┐Х©≤Ф╡║Ф²╔Е╬≈Е▐┼Е▌╩Е╝·Г▌╟О╪▄Х─▄Д╦█Ф≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨Д╩√Е│ Д╦█Е┬╟Ц─┌Х─▄ PhonegapО╪▄Е╝┐Г └Г╩┬Ф·│Г⌡╝Г └Е╟╠Ф≤╞Ф╤┬Е╓╠Е°╗ Web Ф═┤Е┤├Г └Х┐▄Е░▌Ц─┌Ц─█</a></p>

<p>Е°╗Д╦█Д╦╒Е╓╠ web Г └Е╪─Ф■╬Г│╣И╜┌О╪▄Е°╗Д╦█И°─Х╕│Д╬²И²═ Hybrid Ф┼┼Е╨■Г■╗Ф■╬Е°╗ App Store Г └Е┴█Ф▐░Д╦▀О╪▄Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Х┐╫Е╓÷Ф╦░Х©⌡Е╪▐Е°╟Х╥ЁХ└╠Е┤╨Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Г └Ф═┤Г╜╬О╪▄Е▐≤Ф┬░Г■╗Ф┬╥Г°╪Д╦╜Г └ AppЦ─┌Х©≥Ф≤╞ Alex Russell Е°╗ 2015 Е╧╢Ф▐░Е┤╨ PWA Ф╕┌Е©╣Г └<a href="https://infrequently.org/2015/06/progressive-apps-escaping-tabs-without-losing-our-soul/" title="Progressive Web Apps: Escaping Tabs Without Losing Our Soul">Е▌÷Е╖■</a>Ц─┌</p>

<p>Х─▄Е▐┬Ф╜ёЕ⌡═Д╦╨ web Ф≤╞Д╦─Д╦╙Ф∙╢Д╫⌠О╪▄PWA Е▐╞Д╩╔Е┬╘Г■╗Г └Ф┼─Ф°╞Х©°Д╦█Ф╜╒Д╦┼Х©╟Г └Е┤═Д╦╙Х─▄Е╥╡О╪ AjaxЦ─│Е⌠█Е╨■Е╪▐Х╝╬Х╝║Ц─│JavaScript Ф║├Ф·╤Ц─│ECMAScript NextЦ─│CSS NextЦ─│HoudiniЦ─│Indexed DBЦ─│Device APIsЦ─│Web BluetoothЦ─│Web SocketЦ─│Web PaymentЦ─│<a href="https://wicg.github.io/BackgroundSync/spec/" title="Web Background Synchronization - WICG">Е╜╣Е▄√</a>Д╦╜Г └ <a href="developers.google.com/web/updates/2015/12/background-sync" title="Background Sync - Google Developers">Background Sync API</a>Ц─│<a href="https://streams.spec.whatwg.org/" title="Streams">Streams</a>Ц─│WebVRБ─╕Б─╕Е╪─Ф■╬ Web Д╦√Г∙▄ 27 Е╧╢Ф²╔Г └Е▐▒Е╠∙Д╩╔Е▐┼Ф°╙Ф²╔Г └Д╦─Е┬┤О╪▄И┐╫Д╦▌ PWA Е╓╘Д╫°Д╧▀Е░┬Ц─┌</p>

<h2 id="И╠╪Д╦▌Г├┼Ф▌▄Г └Е┘╪Е╬≈">И╠╪Д╦▌Г├┼Ф▌▄Г └Е┘╪Е╬≈</h2>

<p>Г╩▐Х©┤Е┤═Е╧╢Ф²╔Г └Ф▒╦Г╢╒О╪▄Ф∙╢Д╦╙Д╨▓Х│■Г╫▒Х║▄Д╦ Д╩©Д╫⌡Е°╗Ц─▄Web Е╨■Г■╗ vs. Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ц─█Х©≥Д╦╙И≈╝И╒≤Д╦┼Х╬╬Ф┬░Д╨├Е┘╠Х╞├О╪ </p>

<ul>
  <li>web Е╨■Г■╗Ф≤╞И╠╪О╪ Х©╜Д╩ёЕ©╚О╪▄Х▌╥Е▐√Г■╗Ф┬╥Ф┬░Ф°╛Д╫▌О╪⌡Х╥╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Е╪╨Д╫⌠И╙▄Е╪╠О╪▄Е╪─Е▐▒Ф┬░Ф°╛Д╫▌Ц─┌<strong>И─┌Е░┬Ф▀┴Ф√╟</strong>Ц─┌</li>
  <li>Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ф≤╞Г├┼Ф▌▄О╪ Х©╜Д╩ёФ┘╒О╪▄Х▌╥Е▐√Г■╗Ф┬╥Ф┬░Ф°╛И╚≤О╪⌡Х╥╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Е╪╠Д╫⌠И╙▄Е╪╨О╪▄Е╪─Е▐▒Ф┬░Ф°╛И╚≤Ц─┌<strong>И─┌Е░┬Д©²Ф╢╩</strong>Ц─┌</li>
</ul>

<p>Х╕│Г÷╔И│⌠О╪▄Х≥╫Г└╤Г■╗Ф┬╥Х┼╠Е°╗Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╦┼Г └Ф≈╤И≈╢Х╕│Ф≤▌Ф≤╬Е╓ Д╨▌ web Е╨■Г■╗О╪▄Д╫├Е┘╤Д╦╜<a href="http://marketingland.com/report-mobile-users-spend-80-percent-time-just-five-apps-116858" title="Report: Mobile Users Spend 80 Percent Of Time In Just Five Apps">Ф°┴ 80% Г └Ф≈╤И≈╢Ф≤╞Х┼╠Е°╗Е┴█Д╨■Д╦╙Е╨■Г■╗Д╦╜Г └</a>Ц─┌<a href="http://www.recode.net/2016/9/16/12933780/average-app-downloads-per-month-comscore" title="Half of U.S. smartphone users download zero apps per month">Х╟┐Ф÷╔Ф≤╬Г╓╨О╪▄Г╬▌Е⌡╫Ф°┴Д╦─Е█┼Г └Ф≥╨Х┐╫Ф┴▀Ф°╨Г■╗Ф┬╥Е╧ЁЕ²┤Ф╞▐Ф°┬Ф√╟ App Е╝┴Хё┘И┤▐Д╦╨И⌡╤</a>О╪▄Х─▄Ф°┬Е²┤Г╫▒Г╚≥Х╝©И≈╝И┤▐Е█╢Ф°┴ 100 Д╦╙О╪▄Ф⌡╢Е┬╚Ф▐░ Google Play Д╦┼<a href="https://youtu.be/EUthgV-U05w" title="AdWords for App Promotion - Google">Ф°┴ 60% Г └Е╨■Г■╗Д╩▌Ф°╙Х╒╚Д╨╨Д╦▀Х╫╫Х©┤Д╨├</a>Ц─┌Д╨▌Ф≤╞О╪▄Ф∙╢Д╦╙Х║▄Д╦ Г └Д╨╖Е⌠│Г╜√Г∙╔Ф╦┘Д╦─Х┴╡Е°╟<strong>Ц─▄Ф▀©И╠╪Ф█╒Г├┼Ф▌▄Ц─█</strong>О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌Г╛■Х─┘Г └Х─│Д╦°Е╝╤И≤©И┤▄Ф≈┘Х║▄О╪┬Иё·Г▄╙Ф≈┘Х║▄О╪┴О╪▄web Е╨■Г■╗Е╦┐Ф╩║И≤©И┤▄ГЁ╩Е░└Г╖█Ф╦═И│⌠О╪▄Ф▐░Д╬⌡Ц─▄Д╪≤Г╖─Г └Г╛╛Д╦─Ф┴▀Д╫⌠И╙▄Ц─█О╪▄Г╜┴Д╫═Г■╗Г └Е╪─Е©┐Д╨├О╪▄Е├█Е╪∙Х╞╠Д╫═Е▌╩Д╦▀Х╫╫Е╝┴Хё┘Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/PWAR-014+PWA.jpeg" alt="" />
<em>Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Ц─│Е╫⌠Д╩ё Web Д╦▌ PWA Е⌡╬Г┴┤Ф²╔Ф╨░: Hux &amp; <a href="https://developers.google.com/web/events/pwaroadshow/">Google</a></em></p>

<p>Д╫├Ф≤╞О╪▄PWA Г └Е┤╨Г▌╟О╪▄Х╝╘И╠╪Д╦▌Г├┼Ф▌▄Е┘╪Е╬≈Е▐≤Ф┬░Д╨├Е▐╞Х┐╫ Б─■Б─■ Е╝┐Е░▄Ф≈╤Е┘╥Е╓┤Д╨├ web Е╨■Г■╗Д╦▌Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Г └Д╪≤Г┌╧О╪▄Ф°┴Г²─Х┤╙Е╥╠Г▀╛Ф°┴Г └Е┘┬Х©⌡Ф─╖О╪ Ц─▄Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗ -&gt; Ф╥╩Е┼═Х┤ЁД╦╩Е╠▐/Е╝┴Хё┘ -&gt; Е┘╥Е╓┤Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╫⌠И╙▄Г └ PWA -&gt; Ф▌╗И─│И─ Г÷╔ -&gt; Е┘╥Е╓┤Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Д╫⌠И╙▄Г └ PWAЦ─█О╪▄PWA Х┤╙Х╨╚Е╟╠Е▄┘Е░╚Г²─Д╩▌Ф▀┴Ф√╟Е┬╟Д©²Ф╢╩Г └И≈╜Г▌╞Ц─┌</p>

<p>И≥╓Ф╜╓Д╧▀Е╓√О╪▄PWA Х©≤Г╩╖Ф┴©Д╨├ web Е╨■Г■╗Г └Е▐╕Е╓√Д╦╓Е╓╖Д╪≤Г┌╧О╪ <strong>Ф≈═И°─Е┘┬Д╩≤Е┤╨Е┤═Е█│Е┘├Г └Д╦▀Х╫╫Е╝┴Хё┘Ф┬░Ф°╛Е█ЁЕ▐╞Е╪─Е╖▀Д╫©Г■╗</strong>О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼<strong>Д╦█И°─Х╕│Г╩▐Х©┤Е╨■Г■╗Х╤┘Е╦┌Е╝║Ф═╦Е╟╠Е▐╞Д╩╔Е▐▒Е╦┐Ф√╟Г┴┬Ф°╛</strong>Ц─┌Ф┴─Д╩╔О╪▄PWA Е▐╞Д╩╔Г╖╟Е╬≈Д╦┼Ф≤╞Д╦─Г╖█Ц─▄Ф╣│Е╪▐Е╨■Г■╗О╪┬Streamable AppО╪┴Ц─█Д╦▌Ц─▄Е╦╦И²▓Е╨■Г■╗О╪┬Evergreen AppО╪┴Ц─█</p>

<h2 id="Ф°╙Ф²╔Е┬╟Ф²╔Д╨├Е░≈">Ф°╙Ф²╔Е┬╟Ф²╔Д╨├Е░≈</h2>

<p>Е°╗Г╛■Х─┘Е┬├Д╨╚ PWA Г └Г╩▐Е▌├Д╦╜О╪▄Ф°─Д╦█Ф└©Ф└▐Е⌡·Г╜■Г └Д╦╓Д╦╙И≈╝И╒≤Х▌╚Х©┤Д╨▌Ц─▄PWA Е╥╡Г╩▐Х╒╚Е╧©ФЁ⌡Ф■╞Ф▄│Д╨├Е░≈О╪÷Ц─█Д╩╔Е▐┼Ц─▄PWA Д╦▌ ABCDEFG Х©≥Д╨⌡Ф┼─Ф°╞Ф√╧Ф║┬Г⌡╦Ф╞■Ф°┴Д╩─Д╧┬Д╪≤Е┼ёО╪÷Ц─█О╪▄Д╫├Ф≤╞Х©≥Г║╝Е╝·Ф≤╞Д╦╓Д╦╙И─┐Д╦█Е╪─Г └И≈╝И╒≤Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="pwa-Г └Ф■╞Ф▄│Ф┐┘Е├╣">PWA Г └Ф■╞Ф▄│Ф┐┘Е├╣О╪÷</h3>

<p>Е╫⌠Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х╞╢Е┬╟ PWA Ф≤╞Е░╕Х╒╚Ф■╞Ф▄│Ф≈╤О╪▄Е┘╤Е╝·Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е°╗Х╞╢Г └Ф≤╞ PWA Х┐▄Е░▌Г └Е┤═Д╦╙Е┘ЁИ■╝Ф┼─Ф°╞И┐╫Е╬≈Е┬╟Ф■╞Ф▄│Д╨├Ф╡║Ф°┴Ц─┌Д╩╔Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Е├┘Ф═╦Ф²╔Е┬▓Е┬├Г └Х╞²О╪▄BlinkО╪┬ChromeЦ─│OpreaЦ─│Samsung Internet Г╜┴О╪┴Д╦▌ GeckoО╪┬FirefoxО╪┴И┐╫Е╥╡Г╩▐Е╝·Г▌╟Д╨├ PWA Ф┴─И°─Г └Ф┴─Ф°┴Е┘ЁИ■╝Ф┼─Ф°╞О╪┬П÷▒▐П÷▒▐П÷▒▐О╪┴О╪▄Е╧╤Е╥╡Г╩▐Е╪─Е╖▀Ф▌╒Е╞╩Ф⌡╢Е╓ Г └Е▐╞Х┐╫Ф─╖Ц─┌EdgeHTMLО╪┬EdgeО╪┴<a href="https://blogs.windows.com/msedgedev/2016/07/08/the-progress-of-web-apps/" title="The Progress of Web Apps - MSEdgeDev Blog">Г╝─Г⌡╢Г╖╞Ф·│Е╬≈Д╦█Х┐╫Ф⌡╢Г╖╞Ф·│Д╨├</a>О╪▄Ф┴─Ф°┴Г └Г┴╧Ф─╖И┐╫Е╥╡Г╩▐Е╓└Д╨▌Ц─▄Ф╜ёЕ°╗Е╪─Е▐▒Д╦╜Ц─█Г └<a href="https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/platform/status/" title="Microsoft Edge web platform features status">Г┼╤Ф─│</a>Ц─┌Ф°─Е╓╖Г └Г╩┼Х└ Г÷ЁД╩█Г└╤Ф²╔Х┤╙Д╨▌ WebkitО╪┬SafariО╪┴О╪▄Е╟╓Е┘╤Ф≤╞Е°╗ iOS Д╦┼О╪▄Д╦┼Х©╟Г └Е⌡⌡Д╦╙ API И┐╫Ф°╙Е╬≈Е┬╟Ф■╞Ф▄│О╪▄Х─▄Д╦■Г■╠Д╨▌Е╧ЁЕ▐╟И≥░Е┬╤О╪▄Г╛╛Д╦┴Ф√╧Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Д╧÷Ф≈═ФЁ∙Е°╗ iOS Д╦┼Ф■╞Ф▄│Ц─┌О╪┬<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/WindowsForBusiness/End-of-IE-support" title="Internet Explorer End of Support">Д╩─Д╧┬Д╫═Х╞╢ IEО╪÷</a>О╪┴</p>

<p>Д╦█Х©┤О╪▄Д╧÷Д╦█Х╕│Ф╟■И╕│О╪▄Webkit Д╦█Д╫├Е°╗Е╝┐ <a href="https://trac.webkit.org/wiki/FiveYearPlanFall2015">2015 Е╧╢Е▐▒Е╦┐Г └Д╨■Е╧╢Х╝║Е┬▓</a>И┤▄Ф▐░Е┬╟Д╨├ Service WorkerО╪▄Ф⌡╢Ф≤╞Е╥╡Г╩▐Е°╗Ф°─Х©▒Е╝·Г▌╟Д╨├ Service Worker Ф┴─<a href="https://jakearchibald.github.io/isserviceworkerready/" title="Is Service Worker Ready?">Д╬²Х╣√</a>Г └ RequestЦ─│Response Д╦▌ Fetch APIО╪▄Х©≤Ф┼┼ Service Worker Д╦▌ Web App Manifest Г╨╥Г╨╥<a href="https://webkit.org/status/" title="Webkit Feature Status">Е┬≈Е┘╔Д╨├Ц─▄Ф╜ёЕ°╗Х─┐Х≥▒Ц─█</a>Г └ API Д╦╜О╪⌡Х╕│Г÷╔И│⌠О╪▄Webkit Е▐╞Ф≤╞Ф┼┼ Web Components Д╦╜Г └ HTML Imports Г⌡╢Ф▌╔<a href="https://webkit.org/status/#specification-web-components" title="HTML Imports - Not Considering">Е┬≈Е┬╟Ц─▄Д╦█Х─┐Х≥▒Ц─█И┤▄Е▌╩Д╨├</a>Б─╕Б─╕О╪┬Е┘╤Е╝· Firefox Д╧÷Ф≤╞О╪┴</p>

<p>Ф⌡╢Д╫∙Е├╣О╪▄Г■╠Д╨▌ web Г╓╬Е▄╨Д╦─Г⌡╢Д╩╔Ф²╔Ф┴─Х©╫Ф╠┌Г └Ц─▄Ф╦░Х©⌡Е╒·Е╪╨Ц─│Д╪≤И⌡┘И≥█Г╨╖Ц─█О╪▄Д╦─Д╦╙ PWA Е╫⌠Г└╤Е▐╞Д╩╔Е°╗ iOS Г▌╞Е╒┐Ф╜ёЕ╦╦Ф┴╖Х║▄Ц─┌<a href="https://cloudfour.com/thinks/why-does-the-washington-posts-progressive-web-app-increase-engagement-on-ios/" title="Why does The Washington PostБ─≥s Progressive Web App increase engagement on iOS?">Д╨▀Е╝·Д╦┼О╪▄Е█▌Г⌡⌡И║©И┌╝Ф┼╔Е╟├Г╫▒Г╚≥Х©│Г╖╩Е┬╟ PWA Д╧▀Е░▌Е▐▒Г▌╟О╪▄Д╦█Ф╜╒Ф≤╞ AndroidО╪▄Е°╗ iOS Д╦┼Д╧÷Х▌╥Е╬≈Д╨├ 5 Е─█Г └Ф╢╩Х╥┐Е╨╕Е╒·И∙©</a>О╪▄О╪┬Ф≈═Х╝╨Ф≤╞Д╦█Ф≤╞Е╝┐Д╩╛Д╧▀Е┴█Г └Г╫▒Г╚≥Е├≥Е╬≈Е╓╙Г┐┌Е░╖О╪┴О╪▄Е╟╠Г╝≈ iOS Г▌╟Е°╗Х©≤Д╦█Ф■╞Ф▄│ PWA Д╧÷<a href="https://cloudfour.com/thinks/ios-doesnt-support-progressive-web-apps-so-what/" title="iOS doesnБ─≥t support Progressive Web Apps, so what?">Д╦█Д╪ Ф─▌Д╧┬Ф═╥</a>О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Ф⌡╢Ф≤╞Ф°┴Г░├Г■╠Г⌡╦Д©║ PWA Д╪ Е╬┬Е©╚Е°╗ iOS Д╦┼Е┬╟Ф²╔Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="pwa-vs-others">PWA vs. Others</h3>

<p>Х╢╨Х─│О╪┬Х╢╨Е╦┬Д©┼О╪┴Ф⌡╬Х╞╢Х©┤О╪ Ц─▄Д╩▌Г╨╞ Web Е┬╟Г╨╞ NativeО╪▄Д╧▀И≈╢Ф°┴Х╝╦Е╓ Е▐╞Х┐╫Г └Г┌╧Ц─█Ц─┌Е╫⌠Х─┐Х≥▒Г╖╩Е┼╗Е╨■Г■╗Г └Ф┼─Ф°╞И─┴Е·▀Ф≈╤О╪▄И≥╓Д╨├ Web Д╦▌Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х©≤Ф°┴Е░└Г╖█Д╦█Е░▄Г╗▀Е╨╕Г └ HybridО╪▄Х©≤Ф°┴Д╩┼Е╧╢Г┬├Е▐▒Г └Х╞╦Е╓  JS-to-Native Ф√╧Ф║┬Ц─┌</p>

<p>Х≥╫Г└╤Ф┬▒Е°╗Д╦┼Ф√┤Д╦╜Г■╗Д╨├Ц─▄Е╓█Д╩┤Ц─█Х©≥Ф═╥Г └Е╜≈Г°╪О╪▄Д╦█Х©┤Ф≈═Х╝╨Д╩▌Ф┼─Ф°╞Х©≤Ф≤╞Е∙├Д╦ Г └Х╖▓Е╨╕О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛И┐╫Ф╡║Е©┘Х╕│Ф┼┼ web Ф┬√Ф≤╞ PWA Ф■╬Е┬╟ Native Г └Е╞╧Г╚▀И²╒Е▌╩Г°▀Ц─┌Е╝┐Д╩╛Е╫⌠Г└╤Е╜≤Е°╗Г╚·Д╨┴Е┘ЁГЁ╩О╪▄Д╫├Ф≤╞Ф⌡╢Е╓ Г └Ф≈╤Е─≥О╪▄web-only Д╦▌ app-only Г └Г╜√Г∙╔И┐╫Ф≤╞Д╦█Е╝▄Г╬▌Г └О╪▄Е╫⌠Е┘╛Е▐╦Х╣└Ф╨░Х╤ЁЕ╓÷Г └Ф≈╤Е─≥О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛И─ Е╦╦Д╪ И─┴Ф▀╘Е░▄Ф≈╤Е╪─Е▐▒Д╦╓Х─┘Ц─┌<a href="https://cloudfour.com/thinks/progressive-web-apps-simply-make-sense/?utm_source=mobilewebweekly&amp;utm_medium=email#fn-4857-1" title="Progressive Web Apps Simply Make Sense">Е╫⌠Г└╤О╪▄Ф≈═Х╝╨Д╦▌Д╦█Д╦▌Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Е╞╧Ф╞■О╪▄PWA Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Е▐≤Е╬≈Д╫⌠И╙▄Ф⌡╢Е╔╫Х©≥Д╩╤Д╨▀Ф°╛Х╨╚Ф≤╞Ф╞▀Е╨╦Г╫╝Г√▒Г └Ц─┌</a>Ц─▄Д╦█Х╟┬Е°╨Ф≥╞Х│┼Ф┼─Ф°╞И┐╫Ф≤╞Ф┴╞Ф╥║Ц─█О╪▄<a href="https://medium.com/@owencm/the-surprising-tradeoff-at-the-center-of-question-whether-to-build-an-native-or-web-app-d2ad00c40fb2#.ym83ct2ax" title="The surprising tradeoff at the center of the question whether to build a Native or Web App">Ф┬▒Д╩╛Д╩█Г└╤Х©≤Ф≤╞И°─Х╕│Ф═╧Ф█╝Х┤╙Е╥╠Д╨╖Е⌠│Д╦▌Е⌡╒И≤÷Г └Ф┐┘Е├╣Ф²╔Е├ЁЕ╝ Е╞╧Е╨■Г └Ф┼─Ф°╞И─┴Е·▀Д╦▌Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Г╜√Г∙╔О╪▄Е▐╙Ф≤╞ PWA Х╝╘ web Е╨■Г■╗Е°╗И²╒Е╞╧И─┴Е·▀Х─┐И╙▄Ф≈╤Ф⌡╢Е┼═Е╪╨Е┼©Д╨├Х─▄Е╥╡Ц─┌</a></p>

<p><img src="/img/in-post/post-nextgen-web-pwa/qcon-trend.png" alt="" />
<em>Д╪≈Е╓ Г └Ф┼─Ф°╞И─┴Е·▀О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼Г╛■Х─┘Г └Д╦─Г╖█Г▄°Ф╣▀</em></p>

<p>Г╛■Х─┘Д╦█Х╢÷Х╢ёД╩╩Е╬≈Е│ Д╦─Д╨⌡Г▄°Ф╣▀О╪ Х≥╫Г└╤<a href="http://zhihu.com/question/31316032/answer/75236718">И┤█И┤▐Г╨╖Г └ Hybrid Ф·╤Ф·└Д╦▌Е÷╨Г║─Х╝╬Ф√╫</a>Д╩█Ф≤╞Г⌡╝Е┴█Д╦█Е╟▒Е°╨Ф≥╞Д╦▀Ф°─Д╪≤Г └Х╖ёЕ├ЁФ√╧Ф║┬О╪⌡Д╫├Ф≤╞И ▐Г²─Г╖╩Е┼╗Х╝╬Е╓┤Ф°╛Х╨╚Г └Г║╛Д╩╤Ф─╖Х┐╫Ф▐░Е█┤Д╦▌Ф√╟Ф┼─Ф°╞Г └Ф┬░Г├÷Д╦▌Ф≥╝Е▐┼О╪▄JS-to-Native Д╦▌Д╩╔ PWA Д╦╨И╕√Г └Г╨╞ web Е╨■Г■╗О╪▄Е╟├Е┬├Е┬╚Д╩▌Д╦╓Д╦╙Ф√╧Е░▒Ф▄╓Е▌▀ Hybrid Г └Г■÷Е╜≤Г╘╨И≈╢О╪▄Ф╤┬Е▄√Е╫⌠Е┴█ Hybrid Ф·╤Ф·└Д╦╩Х╕│Х╖ёЕ├ЁГ └И≈╝И╒≤О╪⌡Е┴█Х─┘Е╟├И─░Ф╦░Ф╪■Е▄√Д╦╨Г╠╩Д╪╪ Xarmarin Х©≥Ф═╥И▓┬Е╞╧Х╥╗Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Е▌÷Г■÷Е╨■Г■╗Е╪─Е▐▒Г └Х╖ёЕ├ЁФ√╧Ф║┬О╪⌡Е░▌Х─┘Е╟├Ф≤╬Х▒≈И≥█Д╫▌Е╫⌠Е┴█ Hybrid Ф·╤Ф·└Г └Е╝╧Е≥╗Е╪─Е▐▒Д╦▌И┐╗Г╫╡Ф┬░Ф°╛О╪▄Е╟├ Hybrid Х©■Г▓·Е╫▓Г°÷Д╦╨Г╝─Е█∙Г └ webview Х╟┐Г■╗Ц─┌</p>

<p>Х©≥Г╖█Г▄°Ф╣▀Е╫⌠Г└╤Д╦█Ф≤╞Ф╡║Ф°┴Д╬²Ф█╝Г └Г·▌Г▄°О╪▄Ф╞■Е╕┌Е┴█Х─┘Е▐╞Д╩╔Е▐┌Х─┐И≤©И┤▄Е╥╢Е╥╢И⌡├Е⌡╒Г╨╖Е┬╚Х©│Г╖╩ Weex Г └Ф┬≤Г∙╔Д╦▌Е╬╝Д©║Е╟▐Г╗▀Е╨▐Г └ roadmapО╪⌡Е░▌Х─┘Е┬≥Е▐╞Д╩╔Е▐┌Х─┐Е╫⌠Е┴█ Cordova Д╦▌ Ionic Д╦╓Е╓╖ Hybrid Г╓╬Е▄╨Е╞╧ PWA Г └Г┐╜Г┐┬Е▐█Е⌠█Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="pwa-in-china">PWA in China</h3>

<p>Г°▀Г°▀ Google Е╝≤Ф√╧Е╝ёД╪═Х╬┐Е╓ Г └ PWA <a href="https://developers.google.com/web/showcase/" title="Case Studies - Google Developers">Ф║┬Д╬▀</a>Е╟╠Д╪ Е▐▒Г▌╟О╪▄FlipKartЦ─│Housing.com Ф²╔Х┤╙Е█╟Е╨╕О╪⌡LyftЦ─│Е█▌Г⌡⌡И║©И┌╝Ф┼╔Ф²╔Х┤╙Е▄≈Г╬▌О╪⌡Е■╞Д╦─Ф²╔Х┤╙Д╦╜Е⌡╫Г └ AliExpress Д╦╩Х╕│Е╪─Е╠∙Г └Е┬≥Ф≤╞Ф╣╥Е╓√Д╦ Е┼║Ц─┌</p>

<p>Г■╠Д╨▌Д╦╜Е⌡╫Г └Г┴╧Ф╝┼Ф─╖О╪▄Г╛■Х─┘Е°╗<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/46690207/answer/104851767">Г╛╛Д╦─Ф╛║</a>Х│┼Е┬╟ PWA Ф≈╤И ╬Е┘█Х║╗Г▌╟Е┤╨Д╨├Д╦─Е╝ Г╗▀Е╨╕Г └Ф┌╡Х╖┌О╪ </p>

<ul>
  <li>Е⌡╫Е├┘Х╬┐И┤█Х╖├ iOSО╪▄Х─▄ iOS Г⌡╝Е┴█Х©≤Д╦█Ф■╞Ф▄│ PWAЦ─┌</li>
  <li>Е⌡╫Е├┘Г └ Android Е╝·Д╦╨Ц─▄Е╝┴Е█⌠Ц─█О╪▄Д╦█Х┤╙Е╦╕ Chrome Ф≤╞Д╦─О╪▄Е▐╞Х┐╫Х©≤Д╪ Ф°┴Е┘╤Д╩√Е┘╪Е╝╧И≈╝И╒≤Ц─┌</li>
  <li>Е⌡╫Е├┘Е▌┌Е∙├Е▐╞Х┐╫Е╧╤Д╦█Д╪ Е┐▐Д╦┴Ф≤÷И┌ёФ═╥Е╞╧Ф▌╗Е┼╗Х┤╙Е╝╤Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Ф■╞Ф▄│ PWA И┌ёД╧┬Ф└÷Е┘╢Х╤ёЦ─┌</li>
  <li>Д╬²Х╣√ GCM Ф▌╗И─│Г └И─ Г÷╔Д╦█Е▐╞Г■╗О╪▄Web Push Protocol Х©≤Ф╡║Ф°┴Е⌡╫Е├┘Г └Ф▌╗И─│Ф°█Е┼║Е╝·Г▌╟Ц─┌</li>
  <li>Е⌡╫Е├┘ webview Г▌╞Е╒┐Х╬┐Д╦╨Е╓█Ф²┌О╪┬Ф╞■Е╕┌Е╬╝Д©║О╪┴О╪▄И╩▒Г╖▒Ф┼─Ф╞■Х╬┐Е╓ Ц─┌</li>
</ul>

<p>Е▐█Х╖┌Е█╟Е╨╕О╪▄Г■╠Д╨▌ Google Ф°█Е┼║Е│╔Е┘╗Ц─│Ф═┤И┘█ Chrome Г └ Android Ф┴▀Ф°╨Е╦┌Е█═Г▌┤И²·Е╦╦И╚≤О╪▄PWA Г └Г■╗Ф┬╥Х╬╬Е┬╟Г▌┤Г╝─Г⌡╢Г⌡╢И─╪ 100%О╪▄Д╧÷И ╬Е┘█Х▌╥Е╬≈Ф≈═Ф∙╟Е╔╫Х╞└Д╦▌Ф■╞Ф▄│Д╨├Ц─┌<strong>Г╛■Х─┘Е╔╒Ф°⌡Г²─Ф°╛Ф√┤Х┐╫Е╞╧Ф▌╗Е┼╗ PWA Г └Е⌡╫Е├┘Г▌╞Е╒┐Ф°┴Д╦─Е╝ Г └Х╢║Г▄╝Ц─┌</strong>Д╦█Х©┤Ф≈═Х╝╨Е╕┌Д╫∙О╪▄PWA Е°╗Е⌡╫Е├┘Г └Ф≤╔Е╓╘Е▐╞Х┐╫Г └Г║╝Д╪ Ф²╔Е╬≈Г╗█Е╬╝Ф≥ Д╦─Г┌╧Д╨├Ц─┌</p>

<h2 id="Г╩⌠Х╞╜">Г╩⌠Х╞╜</h2>

<p>Ц─▄<a href="https://huangxuan.me/pwa-qcon2016/#/99" title="PWA@QCon2016 #97">Ф┬▒Д╩╛Д©║Д╩╟ WebО╪▄Д╦█Д╩┘Д╩┘Е°╗Д╨▌Х╫╞Д╩╤Ц─│Х╫╞Д╩╤Е╧ЁЕ▐╟Д╦▌Е█∙Г╨╞Г └Ф┼─Ф°╞</a>О╪▄Х©≤Е°╗Д╨▌<a href="http://phonegap.com/blog/2012/05/09/phonegap-beliefs-goals-and-philosophy/" title="PhoneGap Beliefs, Goals, and Philosophy">Ц─▌Д╩╩Д╫∙Д╨╨О╪▄Е°╗Д╩╩Д╫∙Ф≈╤И≈╢Д╩╩Д╫∙Е°╟Г┌╧О╪▄И┐╫Е▐╞Д╩╔Е°╗Д╦┤Г╩╢Г╫▒Д╦┼Е▐▒Е╦┐Д╩╩Д╫∙Д©║Ф│╞О╪▄Е╧╤Х╒╚Д╦√Г∙▄Д╦┼Г └Д╩╩Д╫∙Д╦─Д╦╙Д╨╨Ф┴─Х╝©И≈╝Е┬╟Ц─┌Ц─▐Х─▄Х©≥Ф┴█Ф≤╞ web Г └Ф°─Д╦╨И²╘Е▒╫Д╧▀Е╓└О╪▄Е═╙Г╖╟Ф┬▒Д╩╛Д╨╨Г╠╩О╪▄Д╫°Д╦╨Д╦─Д╦╙Г┴╘Г╖█Г └Д╦─Ф╛║Х©⌡Е▄√Ц─┌</a>Ц─█</p>

<p>Х╞╥Д╦█Х╕│Х╝╘ web Е├█<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/22561084" title="Web Е°╗Г╩╖Г╩╜Г╕╩Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х©°Е▌╩">Г╩╖Г╩╜Г╕╩Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х©°Е▌╩</a>О╪▄Ф╣▐Х╖┬Е≥╗Е▌┌Е∙├Д╩╛Е╥╡Г╩▐И┤█Ф√╟Х╣╟Е┬╟Д╨├Д╦─Х╣╥О╪▄Х─▄Д╦▀Д╦─Фё▓Е╟├Ф≤╞Д╨╓Е┬╟Ф┬▒Д╩╛ web Е╨■Г■╗Е╪─Е▐▒Х─┘Г └Ф┴▀Д╦┼Ц─┌<a href="youtu.be/y1B2c3ZD9fk?t=1h14m48s" title="WWDC 2017">Д╧■Е╦┐Ф√╞Ф⌡╬Г⌡╦Д©║ web Е╨■Г■╗Ф┴█Г╖╩Е┼╗Е╨■Г■╗Г └Ф°╙Ф²╔</a>О╪▄И┌ёЕ╟╠Х╝╘Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г■╗Д╩ёГ═│Х╞│Ф≤▌Г╩≥Х©≥Д╦╙Д╦√Г∙▄Г°▀Е░╖Ц─┌</p>

<p><strong>Х╝╘Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г └Г■╗Ф┬╥О╪▄Д╧÷Е┐▐Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х©≥Х┬╛Г┐╜Г┬╠ web Е░╖Ц─┌</strong></p>

<p>И╩└Г▌└О╪▄Д╨▌ 12 Ф°┬Г └Е▄≈Д╨╛Ц─┌</p>

